; Regression test for issue #1883: print shows empty lot
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/1883
; When all lots of a commodity are sold, eval print() should not show zero-quantity
; lot entries like "0 BBB {93.00 GBP}".

2020-03-10 foo
    Assets:Investments     10 BBB {93.00 GBP} @ 93.00 GBP
    Assets:Investments                           -930 GBP

2020-03-16 bar
    Assets:Investments                          900.00 GBP
    Expenses:Capital loss                        30.00 GBP
    Assets:Investments     -10 BBB {93.00 GBP} @ 90.00 GBP

2020-04-05 * Buy AAA
    Assets:Investments    10 AAA {100.00 GBP} @ 100.00 GBP
    Assets:Investments2

2020-04-07 * Sell AAA
    Assets:Investments   -10 AAA {100.00 GBP} @ 100.00 GBP
    Assets:Investments2

eval print(account("Assets:Investments").amount)

test source
-30.00 GBP
end test
